working with older versions of JUnit don&#39;t read the current 
documentation and get hung up on the imports. Between 4.10 (at least I 
think that&#39;s the version Eclipse Juno ships with) and the current wiki 
something changed about a few of the imports. Net result trying to apply 
what&#39;s in those docs fails. I&#39;m happy that JUnit is still evolving but 
its helpful if people stuck two minor releases back can find some 
examples that work in their world.

Cheers
Mark

